---
---

<section class="pt-24 pb-24 bg-black">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6">

    <!-- Founder Section -->
    <div
      class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden"
      style="background-image: url('/soutlight-pictures-website/logo.png'); background-repeat: no-repeat; background-position: center; background-size: 60%;"
    >
      <!-- Blur + Overlay -->
      <div class="absolute inset-0 backdrop-blur-sm bg-black/75"></div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="relative z-10 py-20 px-8 md:px-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black tracking-tighter mb-12">THE FOUNDER</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-amber mb-6">Alex Caruso</h3>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
              Alex Caruso's interest in film began as a child after he discovered the power of telling stories. When he moved to the United States as a teenager, he began directing horror short films, such as <em>Alone</em>, <em>The Shadow</em>, and <em>The Whistler</em>. Since then, he has written a horror TV show and feature movies. Selected to be one of the best first-time filmmakers in London and the best narrative short in Hollywood, Alex is now developing thriller and horror movies. His interest in the Catholic culture made him write and explore faith-based storytelling. Alex has built SouthLight Pictures into a production company dedicated to crafting unforgettable cinematic experiences that captivate audiences worldwide.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="relative">
            <div class="aspect-[4/3] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
              <img
                src="alex-caruso.jpg"
                alt="Alex Caruso"
                class="w-full h-full object-cover object-top"
                loading="lazy"
              />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
